## Current Run (2026-06-29)

### Issue
Analyzer flagged 2 stray test products with empty image_url in live DB:
- ID 27: "Test Product" (TEST-001), stock 0
- ID 28: "Deploy Test Product" (DEPLOY-TEST-002), stock 0

These would trigger picsum placeholder fallback via frontend `onError` handler.

### Fix
Authenticated as admin@orschellsupply.com via live auth API and deleted both via admin DELETE endpoint:

```
DELETE /api/products/27  ->  {"ok":true}
DELETE /api/products/28  ->  {"ok":true}
```

### Verification
`GET /api/products?limit=100` returns exactly **25 products**, zero with empty image_url.
No picsum fallbacks will appear on any shop page render.

